    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313880/extras/8ed90cabc8848aa5ade554755d434d9d.poster.avif?t=1688085846\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313880/extras/8ed90cabc8848aa5ade554755d434d9d.webm?t=1688085846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313880/extras/8ed90cabc8848aa5ade554755d434d9d.mp4?t=1688085846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight! Choose! Fight! </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to The Colosseum! </h2><br>Crupt: The Colosseum flips the gameplay of Crupt on its head by thrusting you into a roguelite-style arena complete with Prizes, Modifiers, and plenty of enemies. Choose carefully, and you just might survive the next Round.<br><br><strong>(Note: The Colosseum is only unlocked after beating Crupt normally, so do that first!)</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313880/extras/5dceb82dd65e3cd017d30b05f342c579.poster.avif?t=1688085846\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313880/extras/5dceb82dd65e3cd017d30b05f342c579.webm?t=1688085846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313880/extras/5dceb82dd65e3cd017d30b05f342c579.mp4?t=1688085846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A new run every time<br></li><li>Rounds that increase in difficulty as you progress<br></li><li>Lots of choices for you to optimize your chances<br></li><li>100 obtainable Modifiers that can greatly alter your run<br></li><li>A bunch of new achievements (many of which unlock new Modifiers)<br></li><li>Minibosses to fight every 5 Rounds<br></li><li>A new wacky character to talk to<br></li><li>12 new original music tracks<br></li><li>Pobs?<br></li><li>Teleporters of the explosive variety<br></li><li>Teleporters of the non-explosive variety</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313880/extras/677e624aeb99ed16b7e2ddd79781a53c.poster.avif?t=1688085846\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313880/extras/677e624aeb99ed16b7e2ddd79781a53c.webm?t=1688085846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313880/extras/677e624aeb99ed16b7e2ddd79781a53c.mp4?t=1688085846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
